tool_description: This API helps to query businesses in Free Zones of UAE to create a market analytics site/application
title: Companies in Dubai Free Zones

api_list.name: Consultancy and Bussiness Management - Active Companies
api_list.description: Get all active **Consultancy and Bussiness Management** businesses in Free zones
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://companies-in-dubai-free-zones.p.rapidapi.com/active-consultancy-and-business-management"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "companies-in-dubai-free-zones.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
